===Pronunciation===
*φρήν / phrēn / frane
=== Etymology ===

*Probably from an obsolete [[φράω]] phraō (to rein in or curb; compare [[φράσσω]] {{GG|5420}}); 
=== Noun ===
the [[midrif]] (as a partition of the body), that is, (figuratively and by implication of sympathy) the [[feelings]] (or sensitive nature; by extension [also in the plural] the [[mind]] or cognitive faculties): - [[understanding]].